ABOUT THE SYMPOSIUM

SBAC-PAD, Brazilian Symposium on Computer Architecture - High  Performance
Processing, is the major Brazilian Forum for debates  on  researching  and
development in computer architecture area, high performance processing and
correlatives subjects. Its  realization  will  emphasize  the  integration
between  researching  and  application,  offering  room  for  meeting  the
academic community with other high performance processing users. VIII SBAC-
PAD will include invited works, outstanding speeches and tutorials.


TOPICS OF INTEREST

Parallel, Vector and Systolic Processint
Parallel and Superscalar Architectures
Workstations Clusters
Programming and Compilation Environments
Parallel and Distributed Operating Systems
Parallel and Distributed Languages
Performance Evaluation and Simulation
Specification and Modeling
Real Time Systems
Interconnection Networks
Algorithms
Aplications
Neural Networks
Reliability and Fault Tolerance


